                        <p>You haven’t been eating well for a while - for an out of character month, to be precise. Living primarily off of the continental breakfast for a month will cause malnourishment, and some characters may even enter the RP Malnourished. For each consecutive month you go without eating well, add a -1 modifier to all physical-based rolls, including defense. Eating well for one month will remove this status completely, no matter how long you’ve gone without.k</p>
