                        <h4>Second Wind</h4>
                        <p>You’ve been taking a few hits, but have just found your second wind. After rolling two failed defense rolls followed immediately by a successful defense roll, add +1 to your next defense roll. Keep adding +1 to your modifier for each CONSECUTIVE successful defense. This bonus goes away completely the next time you roll anything other than a success, or if the fight ends.</p>
                    </div>
                </li>
            </ul>
        </section>
